 hardness ratio and HI absorption optical depth\nare correlated at a statistical significance of 4.71{\\sigma}. We conclude by\nconsidering the impact of these findings on future radio and X-ray absorption\nstudies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Jul 2017 19:10:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-23"}
